U.S. Treasury Department Schedule for Thursday, July 14

-- B y   V i n c e n t   D e l   G i u d i c e
-- 
2011-07-14T13:12:53Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-14/u-s-treasury-department-schedule-for-thursday-july-14.html
The following is a reformatted
version of the U.S. Treasury Department’s daily release on the
schedule for Secretary Timothy F. Geithner and other officials:  At the invitation of the Majority Leader Reid and DPCC
Chairman Schumer, Secretary Geithner will meet Thursday
afternoon on  Capitol Hill  with members of the Senate Democratic
Caucus to discuss ongoing efforts to avoid defaulting on the
country’s obligations and find a balanced approach to  deficit
reduction . This meeting is closed press.  Later in the afternoon, the Secretary will meet with the
President at the White House. This meeting is closed press.  Later, the Secretary will attend the President’s meeting
with Congressional Leadership at the White House to discuss the
ongoing efforts to find a balanced approach to deficit
reduction. There will be a stills only pool spray at the top of
the meeting. Please contact the White House Press Office for
additional information.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Vincent Del Giudice in  Washington  
 vdelgiudice@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Christopher Wellisz at   cwellisz@bloomberg.net  